leadingComments.value: WeChat public platform doesn't cares about fonts,
thus any font family decorations are not useful.

trailingComments.value: We no longer need to prefix transform to now;
Actually I don't know why they are prefixed, for
WeChat articles are normally displayed in WeChat.
Editors like Xiumi.us can produce extra semicolons.
